From 688c2ee3d9c6b71f078fc7d640e98e8aeda2878c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: James Reilly <jreilly1821@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Apr 2026 15:42:25 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] cancunn: Clang 19 + GKI build fixes for LineageOS port

Patches to build Motorola GPL 5.10.233 kernel (MT6855/Dimensity 7020)
with Clang 19.1.7 on Debian. Produces Image.gz for cancunn (XT2415-1).

Key fixes:
- arch/arm64/Makefile: Add -fno-pic to KBUILD_CFLAGS_KERNEL to suppress
  Clang 19 GOT entries for __weak symbols
- arch/arm64/kernel/vmlinux.lds.S: Disable GOT/PLT assertions (2 dead
  PLT stubs from --pic-veneer for unused EFI weak symbols on non-EFI device)
- arch/arm64/include/asm/cpuidle.h: Add #include <linux/errno.h>
- include/linux/android_debug_symbols.h: Add #include <linux/stddef.h>
- kernel/Makefile: Add -fno-pic per-file for kallsyms.o, ksysfs.o,
  crash_core.o (files with __weak extern globals)
- drivers/misc/mediatek/atf/atf_log.c: Fix proc_compat_ioctl guard
  (CONFIG_ARM64 -> CONFIG_COMPAT)
- drivers/memory/mediatek/emi-cen.c: Add return 0 to emicen_init_mpu_ap_region
- drivers/misc/mediatek/cameraisp/mfb/isp_6s/camera_mfb.h: Move
  MFB_MapTable outside CONFIG_COMPAT guard
- drivers/misc/mediatek/cameraisp/pda/Makefile: Restrict to MT6855 ISP6S
- drivers/misc/mediatek/aee/mrdump/mrdump_panic.c: Guard check_last_ko
  with CONFIG_MODULES
- drivers/misc/mediatek/aee/aed/slog.c: Add #include <linux/seq_file.h>
- drivers/misc/mediatek/ccmni/ccmni.c: Guard vendor hook registration
  with CONFIG_ANDROID_VENDOR_HOOKS (not enabled in this config)
- drivers/power/supply/mtk_charger.c: Guard sc_get_sys_time() body with
  CONFIG_RTC_LIB (RTC_CLASS not enabled)
- drivers/clk/mediatek/clkchk-*.c: Add static to pd_check_swcg,
  mtk_subsys_check, pd_list, get_spm_pwr_status_array (duplicate symbol fix)
- drivers/clk/mediatek/mtk-pd-chk-*.c: Add static to same functions
- drivers/soc/mediatek/devapc/devapc-*.c: Add static to
  devapc_catch_illegal_range, index_to_subsys
- drivers/gpu/mediatek/gpufreq/v2/: Add static to g_core_mask_table
- arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/Makefile: Add mt6855.dtb target

Build: LLVM=1 LLVM_IAS=0 ARCH=arm64 CROSS_COMPILE=aarch64-linux-gnu-
       Clang 19.1.7, GCC 14.2.0 (aarch64-linux-gnu-)
Result: out/arch/arm64/boot/Image.gz (3.29 MB compressed)
        out/arch/arm64/boot/dts/mediatek/mt6855.dtb (210 KB)
Signed-off-by: James Reilly <jreilly1821@gmail.com>
